Naked and Wade (either Athlete or a team and/or agent and/or designer designated by Athlete, referred to as the “Wade Team”) will attempt to collaborate on the design and manufacture of a new line of Innerwear under the brand “Wade By Naked” or such other brand name as the Parties find suitable (collectively, the “Wade Products”). Athlete may have the title of “Creative Director” for the Wade Products, if both parties find it beneficial, and the title shall be featured on the Commercial Materials only when deemed necessary. During the Term and subject to the limitations set forth in this Agreement, the Wade Team and Naked will aim to agree on the process for designs; the process for approving designs for Wade Products may be as follows:
(1) Naked will develop basic concepts for each Wade Product, which may include initial sketches, to be provided to Wade for review and initial thoughts;
(2) The Wade Team should try to provide Naked with some feedback on such designs approximately ten (10) days after they are initially presented to the Wade Team;
(3) After Naked receives the Wade Team’s feedback, Naked will consider those thoughts and may try to add them to the design if commercially viable, and later, could develop a sample of such Wade Product for the Wade Team’s general satisfaction;
(4) About ten (10) days after the Wade Team gets the sample either physically or through a picture sent by email, the Wade Team may look at it and give more thoughts;
(5) If the Wade Team seems to generally like a sample in writing, such Wade Product might be okayed for making (the “Production Approval”).
